---
// About.astro - Founder introduction
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.4fr_0.6fr] lg:items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:items-start lg:text-left">
        <div class="flex h-28 w-28 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 via-emerald-500 to-violet-600 text-3xl font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
          TB
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg font-bold text-slate-50">Taleah Brown</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Founder, Orange County Webworks</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li>5+ years of software engineering experience</li>
          <li>Based in Orange County, NY</li>
          <li>Every site is custom-coded, not a template</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-emerald-400">Why I started this</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-50 sm:text-4xl">
          Hi, I'm Taleah.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
          I started Orange County Webworks because I kept running into small business owners around Orange County who either didn't have a website at all, or had one that wasn't showing up when people searched for them. I've spent the last 5 years working as a software engineer, and I wanted to put that experience to work for local businesses directly — building sites that are fast, custom-coded, and actually set up to get found on Google, instead of a generic template.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
